\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ronald_Kwemoi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ronald_Kwemoi\"}, {\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999703895807877, \"rank\": 1.4443870835363661e-05, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fisher ran a sub-4 mile while in\\u00c2high school, and he was a two-time Foot Locker national cross country champion.\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 464, \"end\": 470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ronald_Fisher\", \"score\": 0.5539107254219027, \"rank\": 0.7801345948104205, \"text\": \"Fisher\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ronald_Fisher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ronald_Fisher\"}, {\"begin\": 532, \"end\": 543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foot_Locker_Cross_Country_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9975993163872856, \"rank\": 0.0024064607635675248, \"text\": \"Foot Locker\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foot_Locker_Cross_Country_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foot_Locker_Cross_Country_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fisher is the MHSAA record holder in the 1,600-meter race when he he won the state title in 2015 with a time of 4:00.28.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan_High_School_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1756057588620557e-16, \"text\": \"MHSAA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan_High_School_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan_High_School_Athletic_Association\"}]}, {\"